name: Chudjak
description: Chudjak is a memecoin on Ethereum inspired by the “Chud Face” meme, a satirical take on internet culture and societal polarization. It aims to engage a decentralized community through humor, meme creation, and DeFi participation, offering a Web3 alternative to mainstream crypto narratives. The project fosters a community-driven movement, encouraging meme creation and engagement through platforms like X and Telegram to drive viral adoption.
